+    // NDC. Eye 0 -> left half (NDC x in [-1,0]); eye 1 -> right half ([0,1]).
+    // Each half also gets a parallax shift sep*(w-conv) (3D-Vision formula).
+    // The engine's screen-space passes then process the wide buffer per-pixel
+    // transparently. Requires a known SV_Position field; RT must be ~2x wide
