+        // clip space (pre-divide). Then pack into one NDC half: x = x*P ± 0.5*w,
+        // where P (pack scale) cancels the engine's aspect-driven horizontal
+        // halving on the 2x-wide buffer. P is tunable live (mask-file token 5).
+        char l[256], r[256];
