+// [option-C native True Stereo / NO-HOOK generator capture] Read-only walk of the renderer's
+// dynamic-texture / generator registry. The dtw-hook on sub_1412BAACC is a confirmed dead-end
+// (4x base-5 AV: that fn runs concurrently on render workers in an unwind-sensitive context).
+// Instead we reach the engine's live generator (the one created for the inventory puppet-preview
