+// [option-C native True Stereo] PIVOT TEST: instead of building the GPU-backed texture ourselves
+// (which the watchpoint proved is noisy/unreliable), put a valid depot RESREF into comp+0x1E0 and let
+// the engine's auto-loader (sub_1423E7768) load -> generate -> GPU-back -> register -> render on its
